<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink313">
<l>teṟuva tamma nummakaḷ viruppē</l>
<l>yuṟutuya ravalamo ṭuyircelac cāayp</l>
<l>pāḻpaṭu neñcam paṭaraṭak kalaṅka</l>
<l>nāṭiṭai vilaṅkiya vaippiṟ</l>
<l>kāṭiṟan taṉaṇaṅ kāta lōḷē</l>
      </lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Alas!  May your daughter’s desire perish!</l>
<l>Our dear girl has traversed the wilderness</l>
<l>in the region that lies between inhabited lands,</l> 
<l>making our life leave [us] in suffering and despair,</l>
<l>and making our troubled and devastated heart grieve, as affliction kills it.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
